      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just spinning my wheels. every time i think i finally fixed something—my job, my head, my relationship—it just falls apart again. it's like i'm stuck in this same shitty loop over and over. i'm so tired of trying to fix a life that just keeps breaking.",
